      <title>远藤出售 25 亿美元债务为其破产退出提供资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/drugmaker-endo-sells-2-5-billion-in-chapter-11-exit-financing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个月法官批准远藤国际 (Endo International) 的债务重组后，银行出售了 25 亿美元的债券和贷款，为远藤国际 (Endo International) 从美国破产法第 11 章中摆脱困境提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/drugmaker-endo-sells-2-5-billion-in-chapter-11-exit-financing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 20:15:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
